public record GoalType<T extends net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.goal.PathfinderGoal>(@Nonnull Class<T extends net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.goal.PathfinderGoal> t) extends Record
Represents a GoalType with a link to the PathfinderGoal class. You can use this class to cancel goal by type, rather than by class.
